overview: Stanley studies in the all-boys Holy Family High School in Andheri East, Mumbai. overview: Spoiled 18-yr-old Dani Fielding's world is turned upside down when her father gets arrested for securities fraud, and she has to leave her upscale life in the city to stay with her gruff Uncle Sam out in the country. Dani pours her affection into this young horse, calling her Stormy and giving her all the attention she's missing from her unsettled life.
